go_to_point_0_1_north:
# go to point 0 1 north
navigator.info('Moving to 0.0, 1.0, North')
goal = navigator.getPoseStamped([0.0, 1.0], TurtleBot4Directions.NORTH)
navigator.startToPose(goal)
